<P>
Megamates: Combine Jane Fonda and her media mogul fiance Ted Turner and you 
have People magazine's "Power Couple of 1990." The couple topped a list of 
megamates the magazine named in its Dec. 31 issue. 
</P>
<P>
Fonda and Turner went public with their wedding plans recently, saying they 
would be married in about a year. The couple rated highest in the survey based 
on categories including joint net worth, altruism, long-term relationship 
