</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
INDIGENTS -- HEALTH; PREGNANCY; MEDICAL CARE -- WASHINGTON DC; MEDICAL CARE -- 
UNITED STATES; DEATH RATES; BABIES; PRENATAL CARE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA122490-0038 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 326692 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 24, 1990, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
