Department of Special Collections, USC Library; Photo, and today: from left, 
Elizabeth Matson, Joe Rodriguez, Carmen Caddick, Raymond Rodriguez, Frank 
Rodriguez, Henry Rodriguez, Gilbert Rodriguez, Mary Wiemann, William Rodriguez, 
Aurora Wood, Margaret Cochran, Ernestine Garcia, Tony Rodriguez and Albert 
Rodriguez. ROBERT DURELL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
