ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: COUNTYWIDE; 
</P>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY 1990-1991 RESOLUTIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"I resolve to maintain our single-family neighborhoods. We have to learn say no 
to developers and I have. 
</P>
<P>
We have got to maintain our quality of life - if not, people are not going to 
want to live here. I also resolve in 1991 to hire more police officers. There 
is a special initiative in March and I hope and pray that it is successful. As 
the major I will also work to get my other council members to help settle the 
Angels' lawsuits and to make sure the sports arena construction goes on time." 
</P>
</TEXT>
